			</div>
			
			<div class="talk_recordbox">
				<div class="user"><img src="images/thumbs/11.jpg"/>刘韵</div>
				<div class="talk_recordtextbg">&nbsp;</div>
				<div class="talk_recordtext">
					<h3>对方的回答是：1+1=2</h3>
