				</div>
			</div>
			
			<div class="talk_recordboxme">
				<div class="user"><img src="images/thumbs/15.jpg"/>王玉山</div>
				<div class="talk_recordtextbg">&nbsp;</div>
				<div class="talk_recordtext">
					<h3>我的问题是：1+1真的等于2吗？不会是等于3吧</h3>
